worms.model.programs.parser

Class WormsParserBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • worms.model.programs.parser.WormsParserBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, WormsParserListener

    public class WormsParserBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements WormsParserListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of WormsParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
